+# PR-214 Remediation Report
+
+## Thread Classification
+
+- `T-214-01`: actionable
+- `T-214-02`: duplicate of `T-214-01`
+- `T-214-03`: obsolete
+- `T-214-04`: actionable
+- `T-214-05`: actionable
+
+## Code Changes
+
+- Updated `src/policy/approval_router.py` so `build_policy_preview(...)` always passes the normalized approval state into the preview builder.
+- Updated `src/policy/preview.py` so the fallback `preview_unavailable` payload keeps `approval_state` and `requires_human_review` instead of dropping them.
+- Updated `tests/test_preview.py` with fallback assertions and a regression that exercises `build_policy_preview(..., preview_enabled=False, approval_state="manual_review", ...)`.
+- Updated `docs/approval_policy.md` so the fallback example matches the corrected payload.
+
+## Verification
+
+- `python3 -m unittest tests.test_preview`
+- `python3 -m unittest tests.test_approval_router`
+
+Both commands passed on April 23, 2026.
